{"tid":1965114,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★東網揭保就業補貼工資4大漏洞　減薪無薪假僱主賺到盡","createTime":"2020-04-09T09:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T08:25:36.000Z","uid":19454,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1896fc1322026c644722421f1ba2cc9d4e88424f","tid":1965114,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T09:17:07.000Z","msg":"漏洞一.減薪<br />\n假設1月員工工資：2.5萬港元<br />\n4月起減薪至：1.8萬港元<br />\n僱主取得最高補貼9000港元，只要付餘下9000港元給員工，<br />\n每月人工開支較1月時節省1.6萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n漏洞二.無薪假<br />\n假設1月員工月薪1.8萬港元<br />\n4月起每月放半個月無薪假，工資9000港元，<br />\n僱主取得最高補貼9000港元，僱主$0支出；較1月時節省1.8萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n漏洞三.領取津貼後裁員「補貼袋袋平安」<br />\n政府規定僱主領取津貼後，其僱員人數不可較原定少，否則沒收或扣減津貼，但當局提到員工若犯錯仍可解僱。僱主領取補貼後，可聲稱員工有犯錯而用不同藉口炒人，並毋須付任何後果。<br />\n<br />\n漏洞四.僱主與僱員「夾計加薪賺到盡」<br />\n1月員工月薪1萬港元，僱主可領取5000港元津貼<br />\n4月僱主與員工「合作」，調高月薪至1.8萬港元申請津貼，實際只支付1萬港元。<br />\n僱主取得最高補貼9000港元，僱主只付1000港元出糧。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200409/bkn-20200409165743656-0409_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200409%2Fbkn-20200409165743656-0409_00822_001.html&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVVtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=2692ead0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200409/bkn-20200409165743656-0409_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ff3173bcd696bdac7715837e51fb4cfe8861b1b2","tid":1965114,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T09:17:14.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"dc13bb7ee5cb442e3f4cdf8dbd93ba5d5d9fe8ad","tid":1965114,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T09:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97bde8a